## Edge Case Handling

| Edge Case | Handling |
|-----------|----------|
| `get` on missing key | Returns `-1` |
| `put` on existing key | Updates value, moves to front |
| Capacity = 1 | Evicts on every new unique key insert |
| Eviction when cache is empty | Guard check in `evictLRU()` |
| `capacity <= 0` | Throws error in constructor |
| Concurrent access | ⚠️ Not thread-safe (JS is single-threaded, but note for multi-threaded envs) |

