## Data Structure Choice

**HashMap + Doubly Linked List** is the optimal combination:

- **HashMap**: O(1) key lookup → node reference
- **Doubly Linked List**: O(1) node removal/insertion (with direct node reference)
- Single-linked list would require O(n) removal; array shifting is O(n)

```
HEAD ⟷ [most recent] ⟷ ... ⟷ [least recent] ⟷ TAIL
         ↑                                      ↑
    evict last                            insert here
```

