## Pointer Diagram

```
After put(A), put(B), put(C)  [capacity = 3]

HEAD <-> [C, MRU] <-> [B] <-> [A, LRU] <-> TAIL

After get(A):

HEAD <-> [A, MRU] <-> [C] <-> [B, LRU] <-> TAIL

After put(D):  ← capacity full, B is evicted

HEAD <-> [D, MRU] <-> [A] <-> [C, LRU] <-> TAIL
